Titolo: Day Watch (video game)

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Day Watch (Russian: «Дневной Дозор») is a tactical role-playing game developed by Russian developer Nival Interactive, and based on the Russian novel and the film of the same name. It features a group of Light Others trying to combat the schemes of Day Watch.
It is a sequel of the Night Watch game released in Russia in 2007. The game is powered by the Silent Storm engine.